Fast Stacker

DIY cheap, fast, portable, and accurate automated macro focus stacking rail (based on ESP8266 microcontroller - since v2.0) 
which can be used with a wide range of photo cameras, and magnifications from standard macro (1:1) to extreme 
macro (up to 60:1 - since v2.0). To reproduce this project, you need some basic mechanical and soldering skills. 

Detailed tutorial:

http://pulsar124.wikia.com/wiki/Fast_Stacker
